  "page": "Siege of Storm's End (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>There are three events known as the <b>Siege of Storm's End</b>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End\">Siege of Storm's End</a> during Robert's Rebellion.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(299)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (299)\">Siege of Storm's End (299)</a> when Stannis Baratheon besieges Storm's End during the War of the Five Kings.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End_(300)\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End (300)\">Siege of Storm's End (300)</a> when Mace Tyrell besieges Storm's End during the second phase of the War of the Five Kings.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403212234\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.002 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:9520-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403212234 and revision id 199823\n -->\n",
